<h1>State of Texas Proposition 10</h1>

<p class="propSummary">
    The constitutional amendment to authorize the legislature to provide for a
    temporary exemption from ad valorem taxation of the appraised value of an
    improvement to a residence homestead that is completely destroyed by a fire.
</p>

<p>
